><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Why Does the Battery Not Supply Power at Night?</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Why Does the Battery Not Supply Power at Night?</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="1" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="vqABORKB+GISh+sagtgFWAd1rsY=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">vqABORKB+GISh+sagtgFWAd1rsY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="bf3bcdfa-74e0-43aa-b827-098c2625d708"><source>Intelligent scheduling policy</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Intelligent scheduling policy</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">Intelligente [planning]</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="2"><sdl:rep id="W+DLwk9wMfyNoG/kiyT7ETOya9g=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">W+DLwk9wMfyNoG/kiyT7ETOya9g=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="aa6b44d1-29ae-45f6-bc0e-83adb4c45790"><source>The <x id="0" /> dynamically manages scheduling based on the electricity price curve and load prediction.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">The <x id="0" /> dynamically manages scheduling based on the electricity price curve and load prediction.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">The <x id="0" /> dynamically manages scheduling based on the electricity price curve and load prediction.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="3" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">SHGtTxDxhcEFSiquusYE7C1t10s=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="40eb31fd-a8c6-42fc-9588-c9dd05c272d8"><source>When electricity prices are low at night, the battery may automatically charge or enter standby mode to reserve energy for higher-yield scenarios.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">When electricity prices are low at night, the battery may automatically charge or enter standby mode to reserve energy for higher-yield scenarios.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">When electricity prices are low at night, the battery may automatically charge or enter standby mode to reserve energy for higher-yield scenarios.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="4" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">jdnszqh2DQYvFadUbptU0zEBwXw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="f30d6394-74ca-4110-86d4-9db2f91c649d"><source>SOC (energy) limit</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">SOC (energy) limit</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">SOC (energy) limit</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="S6ds+rDl2XBodazZVkH139iaEUE=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">S6ds+rDl2XBodazZVkH139iaEUE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="bc60863d-b193-42a9-ac76-5956d46b693e"><source><g id="3">Backup power SOC protection mechanism</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6"><g id="3">Backup power SOC protection mechanism</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6"><g id="3">Backup power SOC protection mechanism</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="FzX2NYWFQc+jvjyw9JetJw7ABys=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">FzX2NYWFQc+jvjyw9JetJw7ABys=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="8f3a1bed-03d3-4c5d-942c-87f8e84da58e"><source>To ensure the power supply capability in the event of unexpected power outages, the system sets the backup power SOC for peak shaving (for example, 20%) or off-grid backup power SOC (for example, 5%).</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">To ensure the power supply capability in the event of unexpected power outages, the system sets the backup power SOC for peak shaving (for example, 20%) or off-grid backup power SOC (for example, 5%).</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">To ensure the power supply capability in the event of unexpected power outages, the system sets the backup power SOC for peak shaving (for example, 20%) or off-grid backup power SOC (for example, 5%).</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">w7wTWIfj3TjhIfSx/uJLJMAoTDU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="a13598b8-5954-4740-a81a-821584fa97ff"><source>If the battery SOC is lower than this threshold at night, the system prevents the battery from discharging.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">If the battery SOC is lower than this threshold at night, the system prevents the battery from discharging.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">If the battery SOC is lower than this threshold at night, the system prevents the battery from discharging.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="36Xxq1zuwcLHk+qVigBn2gypbpg=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">36Xxq1zuwcLHk+qVigBn2gypbpg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="1709dadd-9c8a-4e3d-ae9d-a49e20d3afb7"><source><g id="6">End-of-discharge SOC</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9"><g id="6">End-of-discharge SOC</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">SOC bij einde ontladen</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9"><sdl:rep id="hUZZq50gQbhGZ9jtni6CjIwXMo8=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">hUZZq50gQbhGZ9jtni6CjIwXMo8=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="a5807773-41c0-4510-8022-fbd9f4be3702"><source>If the battery SOC decreases to the end-of-discharge SOC (for example, 10%), the system forcibly stops discharging to prevent overdischarge.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">If the battery SOC decreases to the end-of-discharge SOC (for example, 10%), the system forcibly stops discharging to prevent overdischarge.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">If the battery SOC decreases to the end-of-discharge SOC (for example, 10%), the system forcibly stops discharging to prevent overdischarge.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="Q7R9uJNJQqbjl5J2WC+5RWJPC9Y=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Q7R9uJNJQqbjl5J2WC+5RWJPC9Y=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="533c7070-134b-40be-8226-51a0b7aa3c5d"><source>Operating mode and configuration restrictions</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">Operating mode and configuration restrictions</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">Operating mode and configuration restrictions</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">VivauJpLQFdeBrhbzPiGSWkAbco=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="410c14a3-d773-46f4-b585-be2634013cde"><source><g id="10">Incorrect time segment configuration in <x id="8" /> mode</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12"><g id="10">Incorrect time segment configuration in <x id="8" /> mode</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12"><g id="10">Incorrect time segment configuration in <x id="8" /> mode</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="12" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">qEFaiVGYtEyVDK5wGrvqCQzTtdY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="fb0be185-4300-4887-9fde-bcda9644f212"><source>If nighttime is not set as the discharge time segment, the battery does not discharge by default.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">If nighttime is not set as the discharge time segment, the battery does not discharge by default.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">If nighttime is not set as the discharge time segment, the battery does not discharge by default.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="13" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">rSfgDEZ8MEXVd1BODxMiHiH6PVo=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="f8d6b806-360f-4092-af72-bcd2a17e72d1"><source>For example, if the discharge period only spans 14:00–24:00, the battery does not supply power after midnight.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">For example, if the discharge period only spans 14:00–24:00, the battery does not supply power after midnight.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">For example, if the discharge period only spans 14:00–24:00, the battery does not supply power after midnight.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="14" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">jbvBWfg8WN1qB2lNhTAP1fHJsJk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="66fb3c3a-3d11-4675-95c0-8f887e595cb4"><source><g id="14"><x id="12" /> disabled</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15"><g id="14"><x id="12" /> disabled</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">Uitschakelen</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="15"><sdl:rep id="LC0vmNaTHyvyQVMYtHZDxIuUDcU=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">LC0vmNaTHyvyQVMYtHZDxIuUDcU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b4508f5e-9a1c-4592-b49d-86f46d4c0409"><source>In <x id="15" /> mode, if <x id="16" /> is not manually enabled, the battery cannot charge from the grid at night.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16">In <x id="15" /> mode, if <x id="16" /> is not manually enabled, the battery cannot charge from the grid at night.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16">In <x id="15" /> mode, if <x id="16" /> is not manually enabled, the battery cannot charge from the grid at night.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="16" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">4MNqF54xtZSX8Du4K+WYHz5Jo/8=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d7fca868-acc7-4442-ae5f-705aac1eb0f0"><source>Consequently, the battery may not discharge due to insufficient energy.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">Consequently, the battery may not discharge due to insufficient energy.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">Consequently, the battery may not discharge due to insufficient energy.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="17" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">3J/xnUkuV1njE3Z0r2g7i81EFEE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group></body></file></xliff>